TUTORIAL: OSC Communication

- this document deals (note: WILL deal) with OSC communication between SuperCollider and Python
- use ultra minimal version of soundvase project as a 

Installing OSC Library for Python
- first, clone the following git repository
$ git clone https://github.com/gardaud/pyOSC.git
- then do:
$ sudo python ./setup.py install


* OSC Python libraries

- currently using pyOSC, but there are others:
- scosc, python OSC for supercollider: http://www.patrickkidd.com/
SC 0.2, python client for SuperCollider http://pypi.python.org/pypi/SC/0.2

